Package org.eclipse.viatra.transformation.evm.specific.scheduler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TimedScheduler
    A timed scheduler is similar to the UpdateCompleteBasedScheduler but it schedules in a periodic manner.
    TimedScheduler.TimedSchedulerFactory
    Scheduler factory implementation for preparing timed schedulers.
    UpdateCompleteBasedScheduler
    This scheduler uses update complete events to schedule its executor.
    UpdateCompleteBasedScheduler.UpdateCompleteBasedSchedulerFactory
    This scheduler factory implementation uses an update complete provider that sends notifications to the prepared schedulers.
